===================================================
========== Reboot Into Windows ====================
========== Updated 14/01/2012 - Drezha ============
===================================================

~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Contents
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
i. Aim
ii. Requirements
iii. Usage

~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
i. Aim
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
This extension will restart your PC into a bootcamped Windows install,
allowing you to bypass pressing the option key at bootup (so you can
reboot and walk away from the Mac)


~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
ii. Requirements
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
- Alfred.app (http://www.alfredapp.com/)
- Alfred Powerpack

~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
iii. Usage
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Basic Usage
i.	 Download the .alfredextension file
ii.  Double click to install
iii. Inside the Alfred preferences, goto the Extensions
iv.  Change the Volume location of the Windows install - default is /Volumes/BOOTCAMP/
v.   The location of your bootcamp install can be find in the Disk Utility